{"tid":2204031,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳七月赴台　觀塘遊行暴動案被告缺席聆訊　控方申拘捕令","createTime":"2020-09-15T18:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T18:31:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c3b9211bfc5f9e474d760b6669637cddfc0b526","tid":2204031,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"台灣傳媒早前報道，有 5 名參與反修例運動的港人經東沙島偷渡赴台，在台海巡截獲送到高雄，包括被控暴動罪的吳仲謙。吳被控的案件今於區域法院再提堂，吳沒有到庭應訊，其代表律師指今年 8 月 28 日無法以電話及通訊程式聯絡吳，亦未能取得進一步指示，申請停止代表吳，控方則就吳缺席聆訊申請拘捕令，法官高勁修批准控辯雙方申請，保釋金事宜則容後處理。<br />\n<br />\n吳仲謙的律師代表今指，最後一次與吳見面是7月16日，即案件上次提堂時，雙方7月17日亦有電話聯絡，其後律師於8月28日發現無法以電話或WhatsApp聯絡吳，由於未能聯絡對方及未能索取進一步指示，律師申請停止繼續代表吳，獲法官批准。控方申請向吳發出拘捕令亦獲批，保釋金事宜則容後處理。<br />\n<br />\n台灣記者鐘聖雄上周六（9 月 12 日）公開承認曾協助五名偷渡至台灣的香港示威者，五人遭陸委會扣留兩個月。另外，台灣《中國時報》引述消息指，5 名香港青年7月中下旬偷渡到台灣時被截獲，扣留高雄，包括被控暴動等罪的 24 歲被告吳仲謙。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%82%B3%E5%81%B7%E6%B8%A1%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E7%94%B3%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%A4%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=fd06b25a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%2581%25B7%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%258F%25B0-%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25A1%2588%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2596%25B9%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2589%25B9%2F&h=3cc4d24b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%82%B3%E5%81%B7%E6%B8%A1%E8%B5%B4%E5%8F%B0-%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E6%A1%88%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A-%E6%8E%A7%E6%96%B9%E7%94%B3%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95%E4%BB%A4%E7%8D%B2%E6%89%B9/</a>"},{"pid":"609e77749ec8d44e6a7864feead94e24591ee025","tid":2204031,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0a87e2319970394b3e0e2bc843826e853e623fd","tid":2204031,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"609e77749ec8d44e6a7864feead94e24591ee025","tid":2204031,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:08:20.000Z","msg":"勿諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da8edf6266bae1977105bfdba35f54122eab44b","tid":2204031,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0a87e2319970394b3e0e2bc843826e853e623fd","tid":2204031,"uid":191453,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"609e77749ec8d44e6a7864feead94e24591ee025","tid":2204031,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:08:20.000Z","msg":"勿諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:08:36.000Z","msg":"念*"},{"pid":"28e0e032b873712f2c71c98556295e44809de2c5","tid":2204031,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T18:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9676fd321ebdc2a6aab7dc6d3d77a2035f68148a","tid":2204031,"uid":3253